snippet.title: Battle Isle 93 - The Moon of Chromos gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Battle Isle 93 - The Moon of Chromos, Dos PC game produced by Blue Byte in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/battle-isle-93-moon-of-chromos/15260/
The Moon of Chromos is the second add-on to the famous Battle Isle, is a strategy game, War. In this game different new set of units to battle enemies.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
